module.exports = {"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1>Sequential Stories</h1>\n<p>The Show and Tell model is a image-to-text model for Tensorflow, developed by Google DeepMind, that takes an input and learns how to describe the content of images. This experimental iOS app uses this feature to generate a series of captions and create a story.</p>\n<div class=\"videoWrapper\">\n  <iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/HKbVuHrpphI\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"autoplay; encrypted-media\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row sequential_images\">\n  <div class=\"col-xs-4 col-xs-offset-1\">\n    \n  <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/01-bfd02ab247b022500c60bcdff9170b85-15823.jpg\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n  \n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 336px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 178.57142857142856%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\">\n      <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" alt=\"01\" title=\"\" src=\"/static/01-bfd02ab247b022500c60bcdff9170b85-15823.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/01-bfd02ab247b022500c60bcdff9170b85-935c0.jpg 320w,\n/static/01-bfd02ab247b022500c60bcdff9170b85-15823.jpg 336w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 336px) 100vw, 336px\">\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    \n  </div>\n  <div class=\"col-xs-4\">\n    \n  <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/04-2aee6d8f5d0fe0bfbaa9bb48b50719f0-0785f.jpg\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n  \n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 335px; ma